title: Ross Fararr from Ceremony
itunes:title: Ross Fararr from Ceremony
description:
Ross is the lead singer of Ceremony and he was kind enough to hop on the phone with me while on break at school to discuss mischief, problems with authority and numerology. It was a very engaging chat from an enigmatic front man. Brought to you in conjunction with Propertyofzack.com
